lead_paragraph: Chris Wood and Matt Fitzpatrick were both eliminated from the Paul Lawrie Match Play on Friday, leaving their chances of competing for Europe at the Ryder Cup in the balance.

headline.print_headline: Fitzpatrick, Wood Out of Paul Lawrie Match Play
